--------------------------------------------------

15) GERUNDIO (-ING COMO SUSTANTIVO)
******************************************

Swimming is fun.
Reading is important.


--------------------------------------------------

16) LIKE / LOVE / HATE + ING
******************************************

I like swimming.
She loves dancing.
They hate waking up early.


--------------------------------------------------

17) VERBOS + TO INFINITIVE
******************************************

